&lt;li&gt;Utilize SOQL API’s, Apex controllers, Apex Web Services, Apex callouts, and other development tools to build custom functionality that tailors our sales systems to our unique business and operating model.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in technical analysis activities together and document requirements for application Integration and also involved in integration design activities working with architects and other stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and assure quality in all code entering our codebase.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continually evaluate and refactor our existing codebase for increased extensibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn new technologies depending on project requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
