&lt;p&gt;This position is needed to support Twilions globally with their AV and Events needs in our remote first hybrid work environment. As an AV and Events Engineer L4, you will be responsible for managing and supporting audiovisual (AV) technology solutions, remote event support, and executive support for industry conferences. Your expertise in AV technology trends, bleeding-edge tools, and certifications will contribute to the success of our organization&#39;s AV and events initiatives. You will also mentor members of the End User Computing and Operations team in order to mentor and grow the team alongside you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
